        "message": "LU-18977 efalnd: set hstatus on error before kefalnd_tx_done()\n\nCurrently, kefalnd will not return a proper LNet error\nif the connection establishment fails. The remote NI\nwill not be put into recovery, which could lead to LNet\nattempt to connect to it indefinitely.\n\nSet hstatus in other cases before kefalnd_tx_done(), as\nneeded.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: Id2d4fb6ee0ec15b2d31280b83527d2923a3bf17c\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61072\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Zanhua Huang <zanhua@amazon.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Yonatan Nachum <ynachum@amazon.com>\n"
      },
